text: Michael Schulte (born 30 April 1990) is a German singer and songwriter. In 2012, he finished in third place in season one of The Voice of Germany. He represented Germany in the Eurovision Song Contest 2018 in Lisbon, Portugal, with the song "You Let Me Walk Alone". He finished in fourth place out 26 finalists.
